    <title type="html"><![CDATA[[Clojure] インデックス付きシーケンス]]></title>
    <link href="http://matstani.github.com/blog/2013/06/27/indexed-seq/"/>
    <updated>2013-06-27T16:57:00+09:00</updated>
    <id>http://matstani.github.com/blog/2013/06/27/indexed-seq</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Clojure1.2以前の、<a href="http://clojuredocs.org/clojure_contrib/clojure.contrib.seq/indexed">clojure.contrib.seq/indexed</a>の代替として、インデックス付きシーケンスがほしいときは、以下のコードが使えます。</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>&gt; (map-indexed vector [:a :b :c :d :e])
</span><span class='line'>;([0 :a] [1 :b] [2 :c] [3 :d] [4 :e])</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>例)doseqに渡す。</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>&gt; (doseq [[idx item] (map-indexed vector [:a :b :c :d :e])]
</span><span class='line'>        (println (str idx ":" item)))
</span><span class='line'>;0:a
</span><span class='line'>;1:b
</span><span class='line'>;2:c
</span><span class='line'>;3:d</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>

]]></content>
